---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeaderMobile from '../components/HeaderMobile.astro';
---

<Layout title="Regalo / Lista Nozze - Claudia & Jacopo | 25 Giugno 2025">
	<HeaderMobile />
	<section class="min-h-screen bg-surface text-on-surface">
		<main class="pt-24 px-margin-mobile py-stack-lg paper-texture">
			<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-stack-lg">
				<div class="text-center space-y-stack-md">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">favorite</span>
					<h2 class="font-display-lg-mobile text-display-lg-mobile text-primary">Il nostro Regalo più grande sei Tu</h2>
					<div class="h-px w-24 bg-outline-variant mx-auto"></div>
					<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-prose mx-auto italic">
						La vostra presenza nel giorno del nostro sì è il dono più prezioso che potessimo desiderare. Tuttavia, se desiderate partecipare alla realizzazione del nostro sogno di vita insieme o contribuire al nostro viaggio di nozze, qui di seguito trovate i dettagli per farlo.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_80px_rgba(155,63,37,0.12)]">
					<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLvQtTMH4GTQDVuVLWUUU3ixHXRRgHiUQrKeajl7Rarl3BCSy4Am1fT9zvo1v2epLhkNW0ovKcpjaxc0MYwAB4kCfbqmk5m_yUGcPGXUPTY_gtwxeJiwKsUncfvWm6Of0DV2uLZkt4q5IDgnCqF5zIFfD9SgRK6CJz4d92qmddQRiAnMvvoCbdqGl95rmrnilrLHWZnEksD4_dBshzw58Wr6gPNcOx_w8IM6GGLEoMjTeTSRfg-xczfUOX4" alt="Tramonto romantico a Venezia" class="w-full h-64 object-cover" />
				</div>

				<div class="rounded-[32px] border border-outline-variant/20 bg-surface-container-low p-stack-lg shadow-[0_20px_80px_rgba(155,63,37,0.08)] paper-texture">
					<div class="flex gap-stack-md mb-stack-lg items-start">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">account_balance</span>
						<div>
							<p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-stack-sm">Intestatario</p>
							<p class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface">Edoardo Bianchi e Alice Rossi</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-surface border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-[24px] p-stack-md mb-stack-md">
						<p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mb-stack-sm">IBAN</p>
						<code class="block font-mono text-body-md text-primary tracking-widest break-all mb-stack-md">IT 00 X 00000 00000 0 000000000000</code>
						<button type="button" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('IT 00 X 00000 00000 0 000000000000')" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-on-primary font-label-caps text-label-caps shadow-sm hover:opacity-90 transition-all">
							<span class="material-symbols-outlined">content_copy</span>
							Copia IBAN
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-stack-lg rounded-[32px] border border-outline-variant/20 bg-surface-container-low p-stack-lg shadow-[0_20px_80px_rgba(155,63,37,0.08)]">
					<div class="flex gap-stack-md items-start">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">card_giftcard</span>
						<div>
							<p class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-surface mb-stack-md">Lista Nozze</p>
							<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-stack-md">Potete trovare la nostra lista nozze presso i seguenti store:</p>
							<ul class="space-y-stack-sm text-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface">
								<li><a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">→ Giftbox (online)</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">→ Negozio locale</a></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="text-center pt-stack-lg">
					<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary px-8 py-4 text-on-primary font-label-caps text-label-caps shadow-sm hover:opacity-90 transition-all">Torna alla homepage</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>

